quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  3,78,"And indeed, of them is a group who twist their tongues with the Scripture, that you<a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>may think it from the Scripture while it is not from the Scripture. And they say, “It is from Allah,” while it is not from Allah. And they tell lies against Allah, though they know."
  3,79,"No person to whom Allah has given the Scripture and wise judgment and prophethood would ever say to mankind, “Be my servants apart from Allah.” Rather, “Be godly{1}on account of the Scripture which you<a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>used to <span class=""h"">teach<sup foot_note=""79785"" class=""qiraat"">2</sup> </span>and on account of what you used to learn.”",footnotes:1:Literally ‘Lordly’.
  3,80,"Nor would he command you to take the angels and the prophets as lords. Would he command you to denial after you became Muslims{1}?",footnotes:1:The Arabic word used is Muslimoonwhich means those who willingly submit to God, regardless of which prophet they followed.
  3,81,"And recall when Allah took the pledge of the<i class=""s"">(followers of the) </i>prophets, “<span class=""h"">Inasmuch as I<sup foot_note=""79787"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span><span class=""h"">have given you</span><a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>of scripture and wisdom, <span class=""h"">should a messenger</span><span class=""h"">come</span>to you confirming what you have, you shall certainly believe in him and you shall certainly support him.” He said, “Have you consented and taken up that heavy load towards Me upon yourselves?” They said, “We have consented.” He said, “Then bear witness, and I am with you among the witnesses.”"
  3,82,"So whoever turns away after that—those are the defiantly disobedient."
  3,83,"Do <span class=""h"">they<sup foot_note=""79788"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span><span class=""h"">seek</span>other than the religion of Allah, when to Him has submitted whoever is in the heavens and the earth, willingly and reluctantly, and to Him <span class=""h"">they will be returned<sup foot_note=""79789"" class=""qiraat"">2</sup> </span>?"
